item.title: What grade are you in and what classes are you taking
item.dc:creator: @xxlegitxx xxlegitxx
item.description:
@xxlegitxx wrote:

Junior year of high school, so 11th grade.

International Business
AP Chem
AP Calc AB
Physics H
Spanish 4 H
AP US History II
Phys Ed
English 11 H

We have a rotating pseudo-block schedule.
We have 55 minute periods, 6 periods a day, plus lunch.
We start at 7:30 AM, end at 2:20 PM, Monday thru Friday, 180 days a year.
